In exercises/plugins/com.extense.html5.labs/css/brand.css, uncomment the Lab 4
    sidebar TOC styles:
.sidebar-toc { position: sticky; top: 0; max-height: 100vh; overflow-y: auto; }
.sidebar-toc li[data-level="2"] { padding-left: 1rem; }
.sidebar-toc li[data-level="3"] { padding-left: 2rem; }
